description:
Part Time Bookkeeping Position for Local Real Estate Investment and Property Management Company!

All applicants must have a minimum of 5 years working experience in all aspects of bookkeeping, be highly skilled and extremely knowledgeable with QuickBooks Pro, Excel and MS Office to be considered for the position.

Part Time: Looking for someone that can work 2-3 full days per week (flexible on which days)

Applicants must be detail oriented, organized, punctual, self-starter with an excellent work ethic and possess knowledge of the following skills:

1. A/P and A/R;

2. Bi-monthly payroll;

3. Quarterly Federal and State Payroll Tax Filings;

4. Multiple Monthly Bank Account Reconciliations;

5. Year End CAM Reconciliations and Budgets for Properties;

6. Income Tax Preparations;

7. Daily Cash Flow Statements;

8. Administrative Skills (EXCEL/word/filing)

Familiarity with the Property Management Business and Real Estate would be beneficial, but is not a requirement.

Job Type: Part-time

Pay: $35.00 per hour

Benefits:
* Flexible schedule



Application Question(s):
* Do you have a degree in Accounting?
* Are you proficient in using Microsoft Excel?

Experience:
* QuickBooks Desktop: 5 years (Required)

Work Location: In person
